<h1>Our truck flee</h1>
<div style=" line-height:18px">The truck fleet of the company includes truck tractors "Scania" meeting Euro-5 standards under the ECMT resolution, with semitrailers and truck tankers of the leading European manufacturers.<br /><br />
We carry out freight transportation in truck tankers made of stainless steel, thermally insulated, with 1-4 sections and capacity of 21-23 tones, equipped with the necessary facilities..<br /><br />
